      "para_id": "Q000957.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Enlil , king of all lands , his master , Ur-Namma , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , dug the canal of Urim , his canal of food offerings ."
